Articles.Content: I place them down, and they just are these white tanks that I cant right click. Procedural decouplers just have a regular right click menu of a normal decoupler. Any idea whats going on here?

What kind of mods do you have installed? How did you install the mods? What KSP version are you in? What versions do the mods have?

 The main reason why this won't work is because you didn't install it right. Or you don't have the latest version of module manager.

Let me know
